name: Lakkaberry Krumkakes
desc: A classic dessert from Nod-Krai. The batter is put on a griddle and swiftly rolled up, while butter is added and fruits are sprinkled on top. Crispy, crunchy, and sweetly aromatic, it is very popular among children.

value.text: Increases all party members' Shield Strength by 25% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
